            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>How to Turn the World Topsy Turvey</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"Civilization would be put back a hundred years, Republican institutions
                    destroyed, and our country follow in the footsteps of Mexico and Central
                    America, where a hideous and disgusting mongrelism has made the fairest country
                    in the world 'a hell upon earth.'"</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Virulently racist article opposing abolition.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
