                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"Many a foolish young fellow will throw away on a holiday a certain amount
                    of nervous energy, which he will never feel the want of until he is seventy."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Encourages people to save money and health for their old age.</summary>
